snippet.title: WrestleQuest - Developer Commentary
snippet.description:
As seen during our PAX East Showcase, Mega Cat Studios developers Zack Manko and Andy Marsh take you through the first fifteen-ish minutes of "WrestleQuest," a turn based wrestling RPG featuring legends of the ring. Don't forget to wishlist "WrestleQuest" today on Steam and follow Skybound Games to get the latest news and updates on "WrestleQuest!"

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1867510/WrestleQuest/
